---
// About Section Component for INBIOS - Versión Corregida
---

<section class="relative bg-white py-20 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative background elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-20 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-amber-100/30 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-10 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-100/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16" data-animate="fade-up">
      <div class="inline-block mb-4">
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-600 uppercase tracking-wider px-4 py-2 bg-amber-50 rounded-full border border-amber-200">
          Sobre Nosotros
        </span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        INBIOS S.A.S
      </h2>
      <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-amber-500">
        Soluciones biomédicas innovadoras
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content Grid -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start mb-20">
      <!-- Image Side -->
      <div class="relative group order-2 lg:order-1" data-animate="fade-left">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400/20 to-blue-500/20 rounded-2xl blur-xl group-hover:blur-2xl transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-2xl">
          <img 
            src="/img/about.png" 
            alt="INBIOS Technology" 
            class="w-full h-auto transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-blue-500 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 blur transition-opacity duration-500 -z-10"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content Side -->
      <div class="space-y-6 order-1 lg:order-2" data-animate="fade-right">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Somos una empresa de capital colombiano dedicada a proveer soluciones biomédicas innovadoras para pacientes, profesionales de la salud, IPS y aseguradoras con proveedores de talla mundial.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Fundada en 2002, <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">NEWCLIP TECHNICS</span> está localizada en Nantes, Francia. La compañía diseña, fabrica y comercializa implantes de alta tecnología y desarrollo.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Su presencia abarca una red global de médicos especialistas, instituciones y distribuidores exclusivos tanto en Europa, Asia, Australia y las Américas. Actualmente contamos con la distribución exclusiva para Colombia de <a href="#" class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700 font-semibold underline decoration-amber-300 hover:decoration-amber-500 transition-colors">Newclip Technics</a> de Francia entre otras. Además contamos con nuestra marca registrada Terapia BioVac®.
        </p>

        <!-- Key Points -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-6">
          <div class="text-center p-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-white rounded-xl border border-amber-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600 mb-1">2002</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Fundada</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-white rounded-xl border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-1">Global</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Presencia</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-white rounded-xl border border-green-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-1">ISO</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Certificados</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Quote -->
        <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-amber-600 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-white text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-center">
            ¡Soluciones efectivas, prácticas, confiables! Somos el poder del movimiento.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-16">
      <!-- Innovación Card -->
      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 hover:border-amber-200 hover:-translate-y-2" data-animate="fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
        
