          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-4">INNOVACIÓN</h3>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center leading-relaxed">
            I+D. Con su sistema de bloqueo en ángulo variable PROTEBIO, ganaron el primer puesto en el concurso de Ministerio de Desarrollo de Francia. DUAL TEC SYSTEM DTS®.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Calidad Card -->
      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 hover:border-blue-200 hover:-translate-y-2" data-animate="fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-blue-300 group-hover:border-blue-500 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"></path>
            </svg>
